This is because Roxygen 6 now only loads tags for the roclets it is using, and the rd roclet does nothing with the export tag. This is described here https://github.com/klutometis/roxygen/issues/571. This is an incredibly annoying change to Roxygen, but if we don't generate namespace files, then there is no need for the extra export tags in our R sources.

I see it too, because I have Roxygen 6.0.1 locally. felixcheung have you seen this? I wonder if we could all use 6.0.1, but that's separate.
Do you know of a fix?
